AI Virtual Assistant

A command-line AI assistant built using Python and Groq API (LLaMA 3.3 model). Supports natural language conversations and answers questions in real-time.

Features
- Real-time AI-powered responses
- Natural language conversation
- Fast inference using LLaMA 3.3 model

Tech Stack
- Python
- Groq API
- LLaMA 3.3

How to run
1. pip install groq
2. Set your GROQ_API_KEY as an environment variable
3. python assistant.py
4. Start chatting, type quit to exit
